<h2 style="text-align: left;">Changes</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">Doodle reserves the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. The most current version of this policy is available at&#xA0;<a href="https://doodle.com/privacy-policy">doodle.com/privacy-policy</a>.</p>
